bundesbank set new repurchas tender the bundesbank set a new tender for a 28-day secur repurchas agreement , offer bank liquid aid at a fix bid rate of 3.80 pct , a central bank spokesman said . bank must make their bid by 1400 gmt today . fund will be alloc by 0900 gmt tomorrow and credit to account later in the day . bank must repurchas secur pledg on may 6 .